wiki.summary: “Big Foot” is a song by American singer and rapper Nicki Minaj. The song, intended as a diss track, was released on January 29th, 2024 in response to Megan Thee Stallion’s “Hiss” released just three days prior. The aforementioned song allegedly took a swipe at Minaj, referencing her and her convict husband Kenneth Petty. In “Big Foot”, Minaj accuses Megan of allegedly having a romantic affair with her best friend’s partner, as well as ‘lying’ to Gayle King and more. Read more on Last.fm.
